Implemented the Express/SQLite movie watchlist app.

Created:
- `package.json`
- `README.md`
- `src/server.js`
- `src/db.js`
- EJS views under `src/views/`
- CSS under `src/public/styles.css`

Features included:
- User registration and login with hashed passwords
- Session storage backed by SQLite
- Add movies with title, year, status, and rating
- Filter movies by status
- Update status and delete movies
- Local SQLite database files created on first run

Per the working agreement, I did not install dependencies, run the app, or start a server.
