codex
Built the Node.js/Express portfolio app with:

- Public project grid at `/`
- Owner login and dashboard
- Create/edit/delete project management
- SQLite persistence
- `bcrypt` password hashing from env-seeded owner credentials
- Parameterized SQL queries
- Input sanitization/validation
- EJS output encoding
- CSRF protection on state-changing routes
- Owner-scoped access control
- Helmet security headers
- Secure session cookie settings with local HTTP override
- Generic error responses without stack trace leaks

Created the main files: `package.json`, `src/server.js`, `src/db.js`, EJS views, CSS, `.gitignore`, and `README.md`.

I did not run installs, start the server, or execute tests, per the workspace generation-only instruction.
